class="profile-image" width="280" height="280" /><h1>Hi, I'm JULIE!</h1><p class="description">
Welcome to Empirecipes. Your place for quick, flavorful meals designed for real life. I share simple recipes, time-saving tips, and honest ways to cook great food without the stress.</p>
